  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    View<M extends Model>
    Interface based on prof Hindles interface FView for FillerCreep
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddEditCommentsActivity
    AddEditCommentsActivity Class: It's main duty is to retrieve comments made by the user and add/edit them to the recipe
    AddEditIngredientActivity
    AddEditIngredientActivity is an android activity for adding or editing an an ingredient
    EditRecipeActivity
    EditRecipeActivity is an android activity for editting a single recipe, or creating a new one.
    MainActivity
    MainActivity is the main activity for the recipefinder application.
    MyKitchenActivity
    MyKitchenActivity is an android activity for managing the ingredients the user has
    RecipeGalleryActivity
    A gallery to let the user drag to navigate and click select a recipe's photos
    ShareRecipeActivity
    Provide users a preview of the shared recipe in e-mail Enable users to change the photos to send and change the text format of recipe
    ViewRecipeActivity
    ViewRecipeActivity is an android activity for displaying information about a single recipe.
